                       "message":  "MENUBAR-RECONCILE-DRAINTEST: correction — name the actual menu API (#289)\n\nCodex NEEDS_CORRECTION (docs-only). The new snapshots described the File bar as a\n\"direct egui::menu::bar\", but the code renders it via egui::MenuBar::new().ui\n(crates/editor-egui-host/src/lib.rs:655) — #287 deliberately AVOIDED the\ndeprecated egui::menu::bar. Replaced \"direct egui::menu::bar\" -\u003e \"direct host menu\nbar (egui::MenuBar::new().ui)\" in all 4 docs (Status.md, HANDOFF.md,\nplans/BASELINE.md, change.md). A whole-change-set re-grep for egui::menu::bar now\nreturns nothing.\n\nDocs-only; the render_frame drain-placement test and the rest of the reconcile\nare unchanged.\n\nGate: VERIFY OK (7/7), 10/10 arch lints.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e",
